@startuml TheBunny_State_BaoCaoViPham

!theme cerulean-outline

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 14
skinparam padding 5
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam DefaultFontName "Inter, Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 12
skinparam TitleFontSize 18
skinparam TitleFontStyle bold
skinparam TitleFontColor #0f172a

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor       #ffffff
  BorderColor           #475569
  BorderThickness       1.4
  FontStyle             bold
  FontColor             #0f172a
  AttributeFontSize     11
  AttributeFontColor    #475569
  StartColor            #1e293b
  EndColor              #1e293b
}

skinparam ArrowColor #64748b
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.3
skinparam ArrowFontColor #334155
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam ArrowFontStyle italic

skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #fffbeb
skinparam NoteBorderColor #fcd34d
skinparam NoteFontColor #78350f
skinparam NoteFontSize 10

title State Diagram (2/3) — BaoCaoViPham (Báo cáo vi phạm)

state "Pending"  as Pending  #FEF9C3
state "Reviewed" as Reviewed #E0E7FF
state "Resolved" as Resolved #DCFCE7
state "Rejected" as Rejected #FEE2E2

[*] --> Pending : người dùng tạo

Pending  : entry / created_at = NOW()
Pending  : entry / thông báo cho admins
Pending  --> Reviewed : QTV xem xét\n[chưa quyết định]
Pending  --> Rejected : QTV từ chối\n[không vi phạm]

Reviewed --> Resolved : xác nhận vi phạm\n[ban hoặc xóa nội dung]
Reviewed --> Rejected : sau xem xét\n[không vi phạm]

Resolved --> [*]
Rejected --> [*]

note right of Resolved
  Khi vào **Resolved**, hệ thống đồng thời:
  • users.status = 'Banned'
  • thong_bao gửi tới user vi phạm
end note

@enduml

